    "en": {
      "title": "He tells where Vasant Mudalige and others are",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to police sources, the three activists of Inter-University Student Union convener Wasantha Mudalige, Galwewa Siridhamma and Hashan Gunathilake, who have been detained for 90 days by the police under the Prevention of Terrorism Act, are being detained at the Tangalle Detention Center under the Anti-Terrorism and Investigation Division.",
        "The Anti-Terrorism and Investigation Division said that their close relatives will have the opportunity to visit the group once a week during the five days of the week between 9.00 am and 5.00 pm and that they should bring to the center a certified letter from the village officer of the area that the relatives are their next of kin. The director has given a notice in writing."
      ],
